{"type": "article", "id": 8907, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-04-27T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2209, "name": "餐具"}, {"id": 413, "name": "耳机"}, {"id": 289, "name": "玩具"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 1327, "name": "雨伞"}, {"id": 9401, "name": "Monkey Business"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 9402, "name": "Aiaiai"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605215330n4ayhkmtZc0uPObq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\t\"Drip-Free\" Umbrella by Jenan Kazim\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t雨伞为我们带来便捷，但用过后，水滴滴答答也一直是困扰着我们的一个问题。有人设计了雨伞托，来接住留下来的水，而设计师 Jenan Kazim 则从雨伞的形态入手，直接把雨伞与水接触的那一面折到了里面。这个叫做 “KAZbrella” 的伞打开后和普通的雨伞并无二致，但它的打开和收起的方向却和普通的雨伞正好相反。这样一来，既解决了雨水打湿地板的问题，又解决了进出车门等狭窄空间收伞的问题以及在人群中撑伞的问题。<a href=\"http://www.kazbrella.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215313nWqOUXlbcAk9yo4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79487179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215314mU7RJEAybgTfGhu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81623932\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215315ucX4vKGFedRDx1YP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7991453\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215316AO0pgX6FnrLE1lBT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tCausal Stacking Chair by Nendo\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t日本设计工作室 Nendo 最近为家具商 Kokuyo 设计了一款新系列椅子，和别的椅子不一样的是，这个系列的椅子后背上设计了一个专门搭衣服或围巾等饰品的小横梁，而这个小横梁不是凭空突兀的出现，而是和整个椅子本身的结构融合在一起，是椅子基本结构的组成部分。整个椅子看上去结构简约优雅，有丰富的款式和色彩可选。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215317eGMFovscgC1Nl9Hy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215317WCoVuvrLcqO73FaG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215318ethMyGBkObpwU9Zi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215318pBZ9ywfsho1FVaku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215319hq6dCeDQaE0joWvA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215319kvX3xhUmC5Hfwrue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tWhimsical Classic Toys Corkers by Reddish Studio\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t以色列设计工作室 Reddish Studio 为同样是来自以色列的设计品牌 Monkey Business 带来了一套新的经典的木塞“玩具团”，用木塞重现了历史上一个个经典的卡通角色。有木头兵“卡尔”，木马“洛基”等等。这些角色都是由酒木塞作为主体，加上小巧的配件辅助组成。Reddish Studio 和 Monkey Business 近几年一直保持合作，推出各式各样木塞人偶。这些玩偶的价格在几美元到十几美元之间不等，<a href=\"http://www.mnkbusiness.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以买到。另外，这是<a href=\"http://www.reddishstudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Reddish Studio 工作室的官方主页</a>，可以看到他们更多的作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215320xHw8k6c4isqA1BYr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215320nkGb3lLKzPHI98oD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215320XlTSin6FHR8KIoPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521532167jaI1DCvFdzgEpb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215321FBWemYZCpLfhs7ba.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215322HD36KpYWLBh4C0Zf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052153222vS13gUAoZLlnG7I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052153236rqhtDCKeP0B5wSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215323tKhrOjNVQHo6bPzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tModular Headphones for Aiaiai by Kilo\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t丹麦设计工作室 Kilo 最近为丹麦耳机品牌 Aiaiai 设计了一款模块化的头戴式耳机。这款耳机内含多种不同的模块，包括外部轮廓，内部耳塞，通话器等都可以拆卸，最多有 360 种组成，可以满足不同环境下的音质需求。目前产品售价 140 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.aiaiai.dk/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215324qQd9kYFgujSCDNh4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215324IMAjyUKlVJ2ubFG6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215325SIEoPs04WNKpk3yf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63675214\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215325mJ5UwZhWSXONku20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215326yF4AIseS5HK2mrxz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215326Lkyrj83NwVW76Xbg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tHungry Mats by Hector Serrano\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这是一组逗小孩吃饭的餐具。当小碗放在垫子上，看上去就好像小动物张大了嘴巴在吃东西，而当孩子吃完饭，小碗被拿开，小动物则露出了满意的“微笑”。Hector Serrano 通过这种变化帮助父母“逗”小孩吃饭，同时增加小朋友进食的乐趣。目前有小熊猫，小猪和小老虎三款。Hector Serrano 是一家来自伦敦的设计工作室，此前有过多种卡通可爱的设计作品，这是<a href=\"http://www.hectorserrano.com/\" target=\"_blank\">他们的官方主页</a>，感兴趣的话可以点击查看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215327VOcQh83nvqG401Wy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68541667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215327TARStdVEocy0Ig89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215327PsMyI0rJ8g7kFeYa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68541667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215328rBMRfaJOp1cL9uEz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.3375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215328SlsL9ikCGRO2dD3N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68541667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215329epTW7LvMl5nrwihg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}